{"id":82,"parent_id":73,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":82,"title":"John 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"John","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus, on the Sabbath, heals a man born blind—The Jews accuse Him of Sabbath violation—He lectures them on spiritual blindness."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.1","order":"03.06.009.10293"},["b","1"],"And as",["i","Jesus"],"passed by, he saw a man which was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"blind"],"from",["i","his"],"birth."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.2","order":"03.06.009.10294"},["b","2"],"And his disciples asked him, saying, Master, who did sin, this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"man"],", or his parents, that he was born blind?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.3","order":"03.06.009.10295"},["b","3"],"Jesus answered, Neither hath this man sinned, nor his parents: but that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"works"],"of God should be made",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"manifest"],"in him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.4","order":"03.06.009.10296"},["b","4"],"I must",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"work"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"works"],"of him that sent me,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"while"],"it is",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"day"],": the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"night"],"cometh, when no man can work."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.5","order":"03.06.009.10297"},["b","5"],"As long as I am in the world, I am the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"light"],"of the world."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.6","order":"03.06.009.10298"},["b","6"],"When he had thus spoken, he spat on the ground, and made clay of the spittle, and he anointed the eyes of the blind man with the clay,"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.7","order":"03.06.009.10299"},["b","7"],"And said unto him, Go, wash in the pool of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Siloam"],", (which is by interpretation, Sent.) He went his way therefore, and washed, and came seeing."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.8","order":"03.06.009.10300"},["b","8"],"¶The neighbours therefore, and they which before had seen him that he was blind, said, Is not this he that sat and begged?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.9","order":"03.06.009.10301"},["b","9"],"Some said, This is he: others",["i","said,"],"He is like him:",["i","but"],"he said, I am",["i","he."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.10","order":"03.06.009.10302"},["b","10"],"Therefore said they unto him, How were thine eyes opened?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.11","order":"03.06.009.10303"},["b","11"],"He answered and said, A man that is called Jesus made clay, and anointed mine eyes, and said unto me, Go to the pool of Siloam, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"wash"],": and I went and washed, and I received",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sight"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.12","order":"03.06.009.10304"},["b","12"],"Then said they unto him, Where is he? He said, I know not."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.13","order":"03.06.009.10305"},["b","13"],"¶They brought to the Pharisees him that aforetime was blind."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.14","order":"03.06.009.10306"},["b","14"],"And it was the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"sabbath"],"day when Jesus made the clay, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"opened"],"his eyes."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.15","order":"03.06.009.10307"},["b","15"],"Then again the Pharisees also asked him how he had received his sight. He said unto them, He put clay upon mine eyes, and I washed, and do see."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.16","order":"03.06.009.10308"},["b","16"],"Therefore said some of the Pharisees, This man is not of God, because he keepeth not the sabbath day. Others said, How can a man that is a sinner do such miracles? And there was a division among them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.17","order":"03.06.009.10309"},["b","17"],"They say unto the blind man again, What sayest thou of him, that he hath opened thine eyes? He said, He is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"prophet"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.18","order":"03.06.009.10310"},["b","18"],"But the Jews did not believe concerning him, that he had been blind, and received his sight, until they called the parents of him that had received his sight."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.19","order":"03.06.009.10311"},["b","19"],"And they asked them, saying, Is this your son, who ye say was born blind? how then doth he now see?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.20","order":"03.06.009.10312"},["b","20"],"His parents answered them and said, We know that this is our son, and that he was born blind:"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.21","order":"03.06.009.10313"},["b","21"],"But by what means he now seeth, we know not; or who hath opened his eyes, we know not: he is of age; ask him: he shall speak for himself."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.22","order":"03.06.009.10314"},["b","22"],"These",["i","words"],"spake his parents, because they feared the Jews: for the Jews had agreed already, that if any man did confess that he was Christ, he should be put out of the synagogue."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.23","order":"03.06.009.10315"},["b","23"],"Therefore said his parents, He is of age; ask him."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.24","order":"03.06.009.10316"},["b","24"],"Then again called they the man that was blind, and said unto him, Give God the praise: we know that this man is a sinner."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.25","order":"03.06.009.10317"},["b","25"],"He answered and said, Whether he be a sinner",["i","or no,"],"I know not: one thing I know, that, whereas I was blind, now I see."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.26","order":"03.06.009.10318"},["b","26"],"Then said they to him again, What did he to thee? how opened he thine eyes?"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.27","order":"03.06.009.10319"},["b","27"],"He answered them, I have told you already, and ye did not hear: wherefore would ye hear",["i","it"],"again? will ye also be his disciples?"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.28","order":"03.06.009.10320"},["b","28"],"Then they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"reviled"],"him, and said, Thou art his disciple; but we are Moses’ disciples."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.29","order":"03.06.009.10321"},["b","29"],"We know that God spake unto Moses:",["i","as for"],"this",["i","fellow,"],"we know not from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"whence"],"he is."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.30","order":"03.06.009.10322"},["b","30"],"The man answered and said unto them, Why herein is a marvellous thing, that ye know not from whence he is, and",["i","yet"],"he hath opened mine eyes."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.31","order":"03.06.009.10323"},["b","31"],"Now we know that God heareth not sinners: but if any man be a worshipper of God, and doeth his will, him he heareth."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.32","order":"03.06.009.10324"},["b","32"],"Since the world began was it not heard that any man opened the eyes of one that was born",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"blind"],"."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.33","order":"03.06.009.10325"},["b","33"],"If this man were not of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"God"],", he could do nothing."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.34","order":"03.06.009.10326"},["b","34"],"They answered and said unto him, Thou wast altogether born in sins, and dost thou teach us? And they cast him out."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.35","order":"03.06.009.10327"},["b","35"],"Jesus heard that they had cast him out; and when he had found him, he said unto him, Dost thou believe on the Son of God?"],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.36","order":"03.06.009.10328"},["b","36"],"He answered and said, Who is he, Lord, that I might believe on him?"],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.37","order":"03.06.009.10329"},["b","37"],"And Jesus said unto him, Thou hast both seen him, and it is he that talketh with thee."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.38","order":"03.06.009.10330"},["b","38"],"And he said, Lord, I believe. And he worshipped him."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.39","order":"03.06.009.10331"},["b","39"],"¶And Jesus said, For",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"judgment"],"I am come into this world, that they which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"see not"],"might see; and that they which see might be made blind."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.40","order":"03.06.009.10332"},["b","40"],"And",["i","some"],"of the Pharisees which were with him heard these words, and said unto him, Are we blind also?"],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.41","order":"03.06.009.10333"},["b","41"],"Jesus said unto them, If ye were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"blind"],", ye should have no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_41b"},"sin"],": but now ye say, We",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_41c"},"see"],"; therefore your",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_41d"},"sin"],"remaineth."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.1a","order":"03.06.009.10334"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.28.28-31"},"Matt. 9:28 (28–31)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/20.30.30-34"},"20:30 (30–34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.5"},"Mosiah 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.9.7-10"},"3 Ne. 17:9 (7–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.69"},"D&C 84:69"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.2a","order":"03.06.009.10336"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-antemortal-existence-of"},"TG Man, Antemortal Existence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.3a","order":"03.06.009.10338"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-works-of"},"TG God, Works of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.3b","order":"03.06.009.10340"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/11.4"},"John 11:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.4a","order":"03.06.009.10342"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.17"},"John 5:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.4b","order":"03.06.009.10344"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/4.34"},"John 4:34"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.4c","order":"03.06.009.10346"},["b","4c"],["span.small","JST"],"John 9:4 … while",["i","I am with you;"],"the",["i","time"],"cometh when",["i","I shall have finished my work, then I go unto the Father."]],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.4d","order":"03.06.009.10348"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/13.12.11-12"},"Rom. 13:12 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.33"},"Alma 34:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.4e","order":"03.06.009.10350"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.5a","order":"03.06.009.10352"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-light-of-the-world"},"TG Jesus Christ, Light of the World"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-of-christ"},"Light of Christ"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.7a","order":"03.06.009.10354"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/3.15"},"Neh. 3:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.6"},"Isa. 8:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.11a","order":"03.06.009.10356"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/5.10"},"2 Kgs. 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.11b","order":"03.06.009.10358"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sight"},"TG Sight"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.14a","order":"03.06.009.10360"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.14b","order":"03.06.009.10362"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heal"},"TG Heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.17a","order":"03.06.009.10364"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.40.40-44"},"John 7:40 (40–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.28a","order":"03.06.009.10366"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reviling"},"TG Reviling"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.29a","order":"03.06.009.10368"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.14"},"John 8:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.32a","order":"03.06.009.10370"},["b","32a"],["span.small","JST"],"John 9:32 … blind,",["i","except he be of God."]],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.33a","order":"03.06.009.10372"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.22"},"Acts 2:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"39a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.39a","order":"03.06.009.10374"},["b","39a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"39b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.39b","order":"03.06.009.10376"},["b","39b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/5.32"},"Luke 5:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/1.13,15"},"1 Tim. 1:13, 15"],"."],["div",{"id":"41a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.41a","order":"03.06.009.10378"},["b","41a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"41b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.41b","order":"03.06.009.10380"},["b","41b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/15.22.19-27"},"John 15:22 (19–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"41c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.41c","order":"03.06.009.10382"},["b","41c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"41d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.41d","order":"03.06.009.10384"},["b","41d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."]]}
